data.description: NEW PRICE REDUCTION  !!! PRICED TO SELL !!!  Welcome to this stunning Hayden Model home, constructed in 2021 by DR Horton, situated in the sought-after Harmony West Community of Saint Cloud, Florida. This remarkable two-level residence, in immaculate condition, is an excellent find with 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms.    As you enter, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed floor plan. On the first floor, a welcoming bedroom and a full bathroom offer versatile options for guest accommodations, an office, or a playroom. The open and airy living spaces flow seamlessly, providing a perfect setting for entertaining or simply relaxing with your family.     Upstairs, you'll discover the main attraction—the master suite, alongside three additional bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The master bedroom is your private haven, featuring an ensuite bathroom that includes a walk-in shower, dual sinks, and ample space for your comfort.     This home does offer a spacious and functional environment, giving you room to personalize and make it your own. The kitchen is designed with practicality in mind, offering ample cabinet space, modern appliances, and a layout that allows for easy meal preparation.    Outside, the spacious yard provides plenty of room for outdoor activities and potential landscaping projects. This open canvas allows you to create an outdoor oasis tailored to your preferences.    This property's location is a true highlight, being conveniently close to Lake Nona, a hub of healthcare innovation and vibrant entertainment options. Top-rated schools, shopping, dining, and various recreational activities are within easy reach.    The motivated seller has maintained this home with great care, ensuring it's in excellent condition and ready for your personal touches. If you're seeking a modern two-level home in a family-friendly community with proximity to Lake Nona, this Hayden Model in Harmony West is the perfect opportunity. Don't wait to make it yours and transform it into your ideal family retreat!  SECURITY CAMERAS AND WASHER AND DRYER DO NOT CONVEY
